title: Crew Show!
description: In our final episode of 2012 we talk about Larry's modeling career, wiring money to rappers, Zack reviews the Equinox LTZ, we talk about the Polestar Volvo C30, and we do some bus shopping.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
